                            <comment id="18234" author="ndeloof" created="Tue, 27 Jun 2006 02:46:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I wanted to attach a CVS patch but I cannot access sourceforge CVS (timeout)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is the changes I&apos;ve made on AbstractTransactionAspect :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    after(Object txObject) throwing(Throwable t) : transactionalMethodExecution(txObject)  {&lt;br/&gt;
        try &lt;/p&gt;
{
            doCloseTransactionAfterThrowing(TransactionAspectSupport.currentTransactionInfo(), t);
        }
&lt;p&gt;        catch (Throwable th) &lt;/p&gt;
{
            logger.error(&quot;Failed to close transaction after throwing in a Transactional method&quot;, th);
        }
&lt;p&gt;    }&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
